28:33.407 --> 28:35.626
<i>♪ Pump, pump it up ♪</i>

28:35.714 --> 28:38.194
<i>♪ Pump, pump it up ♪</i>

28:38.281 --> 28:40.327
<i>♪ Pump, pump it up ♪</i>

28:40.414 --> 28:44.113
<i>Monogamy is for humans,
not vampires.</i>

28:44.200 --> 28:48.248
<i>Why should I limit myself when
I've got the perfect setup?</i>

28:50.424 --> 28:52.861
She gives me blood,
she gives me kisses.

28:52.948 --> 28:55.168
Put 'em together--

28:55.255 --> 28:57.213
the perfect woman.

28:57.300 --> 28:58.998
Sucking and-------,

28:59.085 --> 29:01.217
that is the vampire life.

29:01.304 --> 29:02.958
Are we gonna work out or what?

29:03.045 --> 29:04.960
Sure, Reggie.

29:05.047 --> 29:06.701
We'll work out because
the damn Assessment

29:06.788 --> 29:09.486
is right around the corner,
and if you fail that,

29:09.573 --> 29:11.097
you have all the time
in the world

29:11.184 --> 29:12.968
'cause you'll be dead,

29:13.055 --> 29:14.274
and I'll be dead too.

29:14.361 --> 29:16.319
Maybe I might surprise you.

29:19.018 --> 29:21.150
Baby.

29:21.237 --> 29:23.936
Lemme get the door.

29:24.023 --> 29:27.200
<i>♪ La, la, la, la,
ooh, la, la ♪</i>

29:27.287 --> 29:30.116
<i>♪ Nothing in this world
is for free ♪</i>

29:30.203 --> 29:31.682
<i>♪ You always pay a price ♪</i>

29:31.770 --> 29:33.728
No! Missy, you have two guns!
That's not fair.

29:33.815 --> 29:35.948
There's no rules!
Suck it!

29:36.035 --> 29:37.688
Ah, no, no, no, no, no, no!

29:37.776 --> 29:39.690
Skrrt--shit!

